{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"AnimationEvent()","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/AnimationEvent","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Construtor</summary><ol><li><em><code>AnimationEvent()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriedades</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/animationName\"><code>animationName</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/elapsedTime\"><code>elapsedTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/pseudoElement\"><code>pseudoElement</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herança:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta é uma <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tecnologia experimental (en-US)</a></strong><br>Verifique a <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">tabela de compatibilidade entre Navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usar essa funcionalidade em produção.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p><code><font face=\"Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif\">O construtor&nbsp;</font><strong>AnimationEvent()</strong></code>retorna&nbsp;o recente criado&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a>, representando um evento em relação a animação.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"síntaxe","title":"Síntaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>animationEvent</em> = new AnimationEvent(<em>type</em>, {animationName: <em>aPropertyName</em>,\n                                           elapsedTime  : <em>aFloat</em>,\n                                           pseudoElement: <em>aPseudoElementName</em>});\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"argumentos","title":"Argumentos","isH3":true,"content":"<p><em>O construtor&nbsp;<code>AnimationEvent()</code></em><em>&nbsp;também&nbsp;herda argumentos do&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/Event\" title=\"Event()\"><code>Event()</code></a>.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"type\"><code>type</code></dt>\n <dd>Um&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> representando o nome do tipo de&nbsp;<code>AnimationEvent</code>. É caso sensitivo e pode ser: <code>'animationstart'</code>, <code>'animationend'</code>, ou&nbsp;<code>'animationiteration'</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"animationname\"><code>animationName</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n <dd>Um<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> contendo o valor do&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-name\"><code>animation-name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> propriedade CSS&nbsp;associada com a transição. É por padrão&nbsp;<code>\"\"</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"elapsedtime\"><code>elapsedTime</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n <dd>Um ponto flutuante dando a quantidade de tempo que a animação esteve rodando, em segundos, quando o evento termina, excluindo qualquer tempo que ela passou pausada.&nbsp;Para um&nbsp;evento&nbsp;<code>\"animationstart\"</code>, <code>elapsedTime</code>&nbsp;é&nbsp;<code>0.0</code>&nbsp;a não ser que haja um valor negativo para&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-delay\" title=\"The animation-delay CSS property specifies when the animation should start. This lets the animation sequence begin some time after it's applied to an element.\">animation-delay</a></code>, nesse caso o evento terminará com&nbsp;<code>elapsedTime contendo</code>&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>(-1 * </code><em>delay</em><code>)</code>. É por padrão&nbsp;<code>0.0</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"pseudoelement\"><code>pseudoElement</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n <dd>É um <code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a></code>, começando com<code>\"::\"</code>, contendo o nome do&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-elements\" title=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-elements\">pseudo-element</a>&nbsp;que a animação roda. Se a animação não roda em um&nbsp;pseudo-elementomas em um elemento, então temos um <em>string</em> vazio <code>\"\"&nbsp;.</code>É por padrão&nbsp;<code>\"\"</code>.&nbsp;</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificações</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Estado</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-animations-1/#AnimationEvent-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Animations Level 1<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'AnimationEvent()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Rascunho atual</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code></code></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><code><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></code></div><code>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></code><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>43.0</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/23\" title=\"Released on 2013-08-06.\">23.0</a> (23.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>pseudoElement</code></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/23\" title=\"Released on 2013-08-06.\">23.0</a> (23.0)</td>\n   <td>\n    <p><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></p>\n   </td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>23.0 (23.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>43.0</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>pseudoElement</code></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>23.0 (23.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também&nbsp;","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/CSS/Using_CSS_animations\">Usando animações CSS</a>.</li>\n <li>Tópicos relacionados a animação CSS, propriedades e regras: <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation\" title=\"The animation CSS property is a shorthand property for animation-name, animation-duration, animation-timing-function, animation-delay, animation-iteration-count and animation-direction.\">animation</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-delay\" title=\"The animation-delay CSS property specifies when the animation should start. This lets the animation sequence begin some time after it's applied to an element.\">animation-delay</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-direction\" title=\"The animation-direction CSS property indicates whether the animation should play in reverse on alternate cycles.\">animation-direction</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-duration\" title=\"The animation-duration CSS property specifies the length of time that an animation should take to complete one cycle.\">animation-duration</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-fill-mode\" title=\"The animation-fill-mode CSS property specifies how a CSS animation should apply styles to its target before and after it is executing.\">animation-fill-mode</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-iteration-count\" title=\"The animation-iteration-count CSS property defines the number of times an animation cycle should be played before stopping.\">animation-iteration-count</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-name\" title=\"The animation-name CSS property specifies a list of animations that should be applied to the selected element. Each name indicates a @keyframes at-rule that defines the property values for the animation sequence.\">animation-name</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-play-state\" title=\"The animation-play-state CSS property determines whether an animation is running or paused. You can query this property's value to determine whether or not the animation is currently running; in addition, you can set its value to pause and resume playback of an animation.\">animation-play-state</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-timing-function\" title=\"The CSS animation-timing-function property specifies how a CSS animation should progress over the duration of each cycle. The possible values are one or several <timing-function>.\">animation-timing-function</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@keyframes\" title=\"The @keyframes CSS at-rule lets authors control the intermediate steps in a CSS animation sequence by establishing keyframes (or waypoints) along the animation sequence that must be reached by certain points during the animation. This gives you more specific control over the intermediate steps of the animation sequence than you get when letting the browser handle everything automatically.\">@keyframes</a></code></li>\n <li>The <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a> interface it belongs to.</li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"Veja também "}}],"toc":[{"text":"Síntaxe","id":"síntaxe"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também&nbsp;","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O construtor AnimationEvent()retorna o recente criado AnimationEvent, representando um evento em relação a animação.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"AnimationEvent()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"AnimationEvent()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"AnimationEvent()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"AnimationEvent()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"AnimationEvent()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"AnimationEvent.initAnimationEvent()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/animationevent/animationevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/animationevent/animationevent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent","title":"AnimationEvent"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/AnimationEvent","title":"AnimationEvent()"}],"pageTitle":"AnimationEvent() - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}